<br>
How likely do you suppose they are going to cripple you by giving a much smaller return on this ability? Mages are a small lot in EQ. They can nerf a high population class like Monks and it doesn't seem to phase them much, so saying they can't or won't because it would outrage the Mage community, seems untrue.<br>
<br>
Here is kind of what I'm thinking: They never really said they 100% intended Mages to get mana back at astonishing returns by reclaiming pets. They seemed to be ok with it for the longest time, but they also seemed to be ok with things like affliction focus items working on slows, mezzes, charms, and other debuffs. (That's the latest little stupid bit from them anyway). So with so many other classes, and their hurt feelings of inferior egos wanting Mages partially disabled, and with SoE often wanting to take the easy way out, and as proved once again today that they aren't afraid to upset even a large portion of people (Shamans, Enchanters, Druids in particular)..............how likely to you see yourselves getting struck by the infamous bat before to long? <br>
<br>
Seems greatly lowering the return on pet canni would be a real easy way to do that, and still say, &quot;well, it was a bug we took years to finally 'fix'&quot;.<br>
<br>
Yeah, I'm venting a little about the affliction changes made today, but with all the other stuff going on, (taken a look at that 32 page Monk thread on their board lately?) I can't help but to think you guys are going to get smacked into reality before long. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=balanzsonofanz>Balanz son of Anz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Abuser of EZCodes</span><br>  Posts: 2840<br> <font color=#333333>(2/5/03 7:09:15 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=422.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Your thoughts on pet canni</span><hr size=1> Moved to Rants.<br>
<br>
